T02TD2305E:245b-1: aa tsintya ma h'a mu dra n'a ma /
T02TD2305E:245b-3: phyag rgya chen po bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhes bya ba //
T02TD2305E:245b-4: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2305E:245b-5: skye 'gag med pa'i chos nyid 'od gsal ni /
T02TD2305E:245b-6: smra bas brjod med phyag rgya chen pa'i lam //
T02TD2305E:245b-7: ngos gzung dang bral yod la mi byed pa'o //
T02TD2305E:245b-8: zab zhi 'dus ma byas la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2305E:245b-10: rdo rje dbyer med kyis 'jig bral //
T02TD2305E:245b-11: drag pas khams gsum 'gro ba thams cad 'du //
T02TD2305E:245b-12: mun khung gter la sgron me ltar //
T02TD2305E:245b-13: ma rig sbubs nas rang rig gsal /
T02TD2305E:245b-14: chos kun rtsa ba byang chub sems //
T02TD2305E:245b-15: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i phyir //
T02TD2305E:245b-16: sems nyid rang byung ye shes te //
T02TD2305E:245b-17: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs rgyal ba'i thugs //
T02TD2305E:245b-18: de nyid ji bzhin rtogs gyur na //
T02TD2305E:245b-19: sangs rgyas zhes ni de la bya //
T02TD2305E:245b-20: gdod nas gnas pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
T02TD2305E:245b-21: grub med sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor shar //
T02TD2305E:245b-22: de ltar rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
T02TD2305E:245b-23: gdal khyab sa la 'bad pa med //
T02TD2305E:245b-24: zag med rnam grol ngang du gdab //
T02TD2305E:245b-25: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa 'di kho na //
T02TD2305E:245b-27: ched du ma byas ngang nas shar //
T02TD2305E:245b-28: 'od gsal chu bo'i dpa' rlabs kyi /
T02TD2305E:245b-29: ngo mtshar rnam sbrul bsam mi khyab //
T02TD2305E:246a-2: ji bzhin ma yin ma bcos bzhin du snang //
T02TD2305E:246a-3: nyon mongs lnga sogs rang bzhin rnams //
T02TD2305E:246a-4: rnam grol ye shes chen por shar //
T02TD2305E:246a-5: de nyid mngon gyur brtan pa na //
T02TD2305E:246a-6: mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo snang //
T02TD2305E:246a-7: gnyis snang rnam pa mi mnga' bas //
T02TD2305E:246a-8: rang don rang bzhin lhun gyis grub //
T02TD2305E:246a-9: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos rnams kun //
T02TD2305E:246a-10: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med //
T02TD2305E:246a-11: 'khor ba'i rnam rtog sna tshogs las //
T02TD2305E:246a-12: rgyal ba'i sku dang ye shes 'byung //
T02TD2305E:246a-13: rang bzhin ma skyes yum gyi klong //
T02TD2305E:246a-14: ma 'gags shar ba yab kyi mkha' //
T02TD2305E:246a-15: de ltar gnyis med bde ba ni //
T02TD2305E:246a-16: rnal 'byor rig pa'i dgongs pa yin //
T02TD2305E:246a-17: bya byed rig pa'i rtsol ba rnams //
T02TD2305E:246a-18: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med //
T02TD2305E:246a-20: lhun grub ma bcos sku gsung thugs //
T02TD2305E:246a-21: 'dus byas phung po'i rang bzhin ni //
T02TD2305E:246a-22: zag med rnam par grol ba dang //
T02TD2305E:246a-24: rang bzhin spyod pa sgyu ma'i grogs //
T02TD2305E:246a-25: gsang chen bla med theg pa 'di //
T02TD2305E:246a-26: thabs dang shes rab phul du phyin //
T02TD2305E:246a-27: snang dang mi snang gnyis su med //
T02TD2305E:246a-28: 'dzin pa bral ba de tsam mo //
T02TD2305E:246a-29: ji bzhin ma bcos sems nyid la //
T02TD2305E:246a-30: ma yengs bcos bslad med par gnas //
T02TD2305E:246a-31: des na gsang ba'i snying po ni //
T02TD2305E:246a-32: tshig gi brjod pa'i yul las 'das //
T02TD2305E:246a-33: rang lus dpen ba'i dgon pa der //
T02TD2305E:246a-34: phyi nang gsang ba'i yo byad 'dzin //
T02TD2305E:246a-35: sems nyid rin chen za ma tog / chags bral nam mkha' ltar du 'char //
T02TD2305E:246a-37: rin chen mdzes pa sna tshogs la //
T02TD2305E:246a-38: 'phrul dga' lta bur snang bas na //
T02TD2305E:246a-39: don du mi 'gyur yongs ma gsungs //
T02TD2305E:246a-40: bdag nyid chen po rgyal ba'i sems //
T02TD2305E:246a-41: rtogs par 'dod pa dgad bro aang //
T02TD2305E:246a-42: khams gsum ye nas rgyal ba'i sku //
T02TD2305E:246a-44: dus gsum rgyal ba rang gi sems //
T02TD2305E:246a-45: 'bad cing rtsol ba'i nang dang bral //
T02TD2305E:246a-46: bde dang sdug bsngal da byer med la //
T02TD2305E:246a-47: spong len mtshan ma 'dod pa ci //
T02TD2305E:246a-48: de nyid rang gsal 'dzin pa med //
T02TD2305E:246a-49: 'dzin med grub mtha' lta ba bral //
T02TD2305E:246a-50: sems kyi me long de gsal ba //
T02TD2305E:246a-51: sngags 'chang dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid //
T02TD2305E:246b-0: rang la gnas @246b bas gzhan du min //
T02TD2305E:246b-1: rgyun du gnas kyang gting dpag dka' //
T02TD2305E:246b-2: rtsol sgrub bral bar yangs la khyab //
T02TD2305E:246b-3: dngos su mthong ba bla ma'i drin //
T02TD2305E:246b-4: ma skyes spros bral sems nyid ni //
T02TD2305E:246b-5: kha dog dbyibs dang gnas rig bral //
T02TD2305E:246b-6: zab cing rgya che gsal bar ldan //
T02TD2305E:246b-7: brtan g-yo ma lus de ltar byos //
T02TD2305E:246b-9: gsal bar yod kyang rtogs pa med //
T02TD2305E:246b-10: sems nyid nor bu rin chen de //
T02TD2305E:246b-11: sbubs na mkha' lding phru gu 'dra //
T02TD2305E:246b-12: dam pa mnyes byed skyes bu yis //
T02TD2305E:246b-13: bde gshegs dgongs pa rdzogs pa'i don //
T02TD2305E:246b-14: dug gsum sku gsung thugs su dag /
T02TD2305E:246b-15: dpa' bo seng ge bzhin du rgyu //
T02TD2305E:246b-16: theg chen gsang ba'i rnal 'byor gyis //
T02TD2305E:246b-17: spyod pa'i khyad par ci spyad kyang //
T02TD2305E:246b-18: tshogs bsgyur len med 'dzin dang bral //
T02TD2305E:246b-19: dkyil 'khor chen po'i gsang bar zhugs //
T02TD2305E:246b-20: sku gsung yon tan phrin las la //
T02TD2305E:246b-21: 'od gsal ye shes snyoms mdzad pa //
T02TD2305E:246b-22: bdag gzhan gnyis kyi 'dod pa sgrub //
T02TD2305E:246b-23: thugs rjes khams gsum sgrol la brtson //
T02TD2305E:246b-24: rol pa'i ye shes dgyes pa las //
T02TD2305E:246b-25: thabs chen zab mo'i theg pa spro //
T02TD2305E:246b-26: mi zad bsdu ba zung du 'jug / de ltar mnyam spyod rnal 'byor gyis //
T02TD2305E:246b-27: rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug ti lli pas go ri shar ba'i rgyal po'i khab tu rnal 'byor pa la gdams pa /
T02TD2305E:246b-28: rang bzhin bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhes bya ba ai thi//
